  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Double Time is a fun and energetic game suitable for any age group. The game is very dynamic; it trains your reactions and contains useful exercises for training your eye muscles. Did you know it? there are muscles everywhere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Characteristics of the game: you will be given a certain amount of time. Every time you hit the coins with the ball, you will be given 5 additional seconds. The more you hit the target, the more chances you have to beat the record, collecting 55 coins<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, it is all not so easy. You will have enemies, that will try to sabotage you by shooting at you. You will need to resist them, keeping the time in mind!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Double Time is a fun and energetic game suitable for any age group. The game is very dynamic; it trains your reactions and contains useful exercises for training your eye muscles. Did you know it? there are muscles everywhere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Characteristics of the game: you will be given a certain amount of time. Every time you hit the coins with the ball, you will be given 5 additional seconds. The more you hit the target, the more chances you have to beat the record, collecting 55 coins<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, it is all not so easy. You will have enemies, that will try to sabotage you by shooting at you. You will need to resist them, keeping the time in mind!",
